  "executive_summary": "Comprehensive plan to fix the 'failed to load projects' error, consolidate styling to house standards, and fully integrate Projects with CRICO (Claude/Cognitive Operating System) functionality. This is a 3-phase implementation spanning styling fixes, database alignment, and AI-powered project intelligence.",
  "phases": [
